title: O'Neill SUP
description: When Jack O'Neill created the first wetsuit, the brand made its mark in watersports, and supporting stand up paddle is another example of our commitment over the last six decades. With the increased popularity of SUP, it's great to see the sport take off from both a casual and competitive standpoint. Adding SUP events, sun-protection products and prominent athletes to our brand roster makes perfect sense and exposes the sport to even more people around the world.
